<div id="aboutwrap">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row centered">
      <div class="col-lg-12 col-lg-offset-4" id="profileInfo">
        <img class="img-circle" src="/assets/samprofilepic.jpeg" width="120" height="130" alt="Icon">
        <h4>Sam Hotop</h4>
        <p>I'm glad <b>you</b> are here! I built this website as a platform through which to share my passions, creativity, ideas and <b>adventures</b>. If you have any feedback about the site's design, any bugs, or would like to contact me for other reasons, please feel free to send me a message. I hope you find the content here fun and <b>engaging</b>.</p>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-offset-4 contact-form well well-sm" id="contact-form">
          <div class="container">
            <%= simple_form_for @contact, :html => {:class => 'form-horizontal' } do |f| %>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactName">Name</label>
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="contactName" name="contact[name]" placeholder="Enter Name">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactEmail">Email Address</label>
                <input type="email" class="form-control" id="contactEmail" name="contact[email]" placeholder="Email">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contactMessage">Message</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" name="contact[message]" rows="5" placeholder="Message for Sam"></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="hidden">
                <%= f.input :nickname, :hint => 'Leave this field blank!' %>
              </div>
              <div class="form-actions">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-block btn-primary">Submit</button>
              </div>
            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="skillset">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row col-lg-12">
      <h1 id="skill-title">My Skillset</h1>
      <div id="skills">
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <h2>Software Engineering</h2>
          <p>Test Automation, Test Frameworks, Security Testing, Tools Development</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <h2>Agile Consulting</h2>
          <p>5+ Years Agile Software Delivery across a number of domains</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <h2>Foreign Languages</h2>
          <p>Fluency in Russian, Translation, Interpretation, International Relationships</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">
          <h2>Jazz Guitar</h2>
          <p>I'm an avid learner with a deep respect for the art.  I love to improvise!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="doWhat">
  <div class="container">
    <div id="greeting">
      <p>shotop labs</p>
    </div>
    <div id="crisscross-content"
      <div class="row centered" style="border-bottom: 2px solid #ecf0f1; padding-top: 60px;">
        <div class="col-lg-6" style="border-right: 2px solid #ecf0f1;">
          <i class="fa fa-comment"><h3><%= link_to "BLOG", blog_path %></h3></i>
          <br>
          <p><b>Life, Travel, Personal, and Professional. These are the ideas and experiences that make the shotop world go round. Interested in being a guest blogger on shotoplabs?</b></p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <i class="fa fa-language"><h3><%= link_to "RUSSIAN TRANSLATIONS", translations_path %></h3></i>
          <p><b>I've been studying Russian language, literature and culture for over a decade. Catch interesting stories from around the web, translated into English by yours truly.</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row centered" style="padding-bottom: 200px;">
        <div class="col-lg-6" style="border-right: 2px solid #ecf0f1; padding-top: 40px;">
          <i class="fa fa-music"><h3><%= link_to "MUSIC", music_path %></h3></i>
          <p><b>Recordings I've made of various jazz standards. I've grown accustomed to my guitar's face.</b></p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6" style="padding-top: 40px;">
          <i class="fa fa-flask"><h3><%= link_to "PROJECTS", projects_path %></h3></i>
          <p><b>Personal projects I'm working on while not building this website, including the fan favorite Psychedelipong.</b></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>